{"tid":2149933,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"即將要走既你","createTime":"2020-08-10T16:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T18:23:42.000Z","uid":311728,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fda3c33af33ddd3e2387f8d6250f959864868f1f","tid":2149933,"uid":311728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T16:28:55.000Z","msg":"如果無中共 如果香港無搞成咁<br />\n或者我地可以好有信心繼續行落去 將來既日子都有大家<br />\n你放工翻黎 我就煮飯比你食 夜晚一齊坐梳化煲劇 咁就一日<br />\n呢啲都係我幻想同你一齊既平淡生活<br />\n一諗到將來可能是但一個要走先 我就好唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次都喊<br />\n雖然而家一齊未算好耐 可能無資格講咁多 亦都可能有人會話「咁後生世界咁大 搵過個啦」「洗唔洗咁快認定一個人」<br />\n我係傻 傻就傻左我鐘意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家對呢段感情都好認真<br />\n唯有珍惜而家既日子 因為無人知幾時係最後一日<br />\n我真係好想同你行到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20bfa9c197322ff50fa4963e5186f06ebd74ab8","tid":2149933,"uid":87461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"我都因為咁散咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDklm呢世都同ccp同港共有仇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306d483c052589ce4546038a8ee6e44f4fe8baab","tid":2149933,"uid":203701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:15:04.000Z","msg":"疫情下個個屈喺屋企胡思亂想 忙讀書個ex派帽俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c81c8c21e66ec860b074bb478534a1a773a5d5","tid":2149933,"uid":311728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c20bfa9c197322ff50fa4963e5186f06ebd74ab8","tid":2149933,"uid":87461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"我都因為咁散咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDklm呢世都同ccp同港共有仇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/f